---
const skills = [
  'C++', 'Python',
  'Unreal Engine 5', 'Linux',
  'Networking / EOS', 'Perforce & Git',
  'Performance Optimisation', 'FMOD',
];
---

<section id="about" data-reveal>
  <h2 class="section-heading">
    <span class="section-num">01.</span> About Me
  </h2>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>
        I'm a Software Engineer specialising in real-time systems and complex feature delivery. I care about
        scalable architecture, measurable impact, and empowering the people around me — whether that means
        mentoring engineers, aligning cross-functional teams, or owning a feature end-to-end.
      </p>
      <p>
        I currently work at <a href="https://www.asml.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ASML</a>,
        developing embedded software for EUV semiconductor lithography machines. Before that, I spent two years
        at <a href="https://www.stellar.games" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Stellar Entertainment</a>
        building game systems and multiplayer infrastructure in Unreal Engine 5. My Masters degree project —
        Khemia — won the <strong style="color: var(--lightest-slate)">PlayStation Talents Best Original Idea</strong> award.
      </p>
      <p>Here are a few technologies I've been working with recently:</p>

      <ul class="skills-list">
        {skills.map(skill => <li>{skill}</li>)}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-photo">
      <div class="photo-wrapper">
        <img src="/images/me.jpeg" alt="Photo of Borja Arán" class="photo-img" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .section-heading {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--lightest-slate);
    white-space: nowrap;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .section-heading::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    height: 1px;
    width: 300px;
    background-color: var(--lightest-navy);
    margin-left: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 1;
  }

  .section-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(var(--fz-md), 3vw, var(--fz-xl));
    color: var(--green);
    margin-right: 10px;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: 50px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--slate);
    font-size: var(--fz-lg);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .about-text a {
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .skills-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(140px, 200px));
    gap: 0 10px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 20px 0 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .skills-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 20px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fz-xs);
    color: var(--slate);
    line-height: 2;
  }

  .skills-list li::before {
    content: '▹';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .about-photo {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .photo-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .photo-wrapper::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border: 2px solid var(--green);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    transform: translate(15px, 15px);
    z-index: -1;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .photo-wrapper:hover::after {
    transform: translate(8px, 8px);
  }

  .photo-img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 2px solid var(--green);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    display: block;
    filter: grayscale(20%);
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .photo-wrapper:hover .photo-img {
    filter: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-photo {
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>
